==致病風險因素==

通过众多病史学和临床研究至少可以总结出一定的、有利于动脉硬化形成的因素。
===後天可變的===
*[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]<ref name=nhlbi.nih>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/atherosclerosis/atrisk |title=Atherosclerosis |publisher=NHLBI, NIH |accessdate=2018-05-11 |archivedate=2017-10-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005113430/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/atherosclerosis/atrisk |deadurl=no }}</ref>
