==預防==
大量流行病學研究和隨機對照臨床試驗證實，[[低密度膽固醇|低密度膽固醇]]的升高是引發動脈粥狀硬化的的一個重要因素<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Efficacy and safety of more intensive lowering of LDL cholesterol: a meta-analysis of data from 170 000 participants in 26 randomised trials|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0140-6736(10)61350-5|date=2010-11|journal=The Lancet|issue=9753|doi=10.1016/s0140-6736(10)61350-5|volume=376|pages=1670–1681|issn=0140-6736}}</ref>，因此推動終身的健康生活方式與飲食能幫助管理血液中的膽固醇。即使是基因遺傳導致動脈粥狀硬化風險較高的人也可通過改變生活方式來降低多達50%的風險。除此之外，保持正常的體重和血糖、減少單醣和精製碳水化合物攝入量與增加運動頻率均可改善血脂水平並促進健康。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Management of Hypertriglyceridemia for Prevention of Atherosclerotic Cardiovascular Disease|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ccl.2015.02.007|last=Brinton|first=Eliot A.|date=2015-05|journal=Cardiology Clinics|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.ccl.2015.02.007|volume=33|pages=309–323|issn=0733-8651}}</ref>

==治療==
臨床試驗證實可以透過以下藥物減少血液中[[低密度膽固醇|低密度膽固醇]]含量進而減少動脈粥狀硬化心臟病的風險：

* [[他汀類藥物|他汀類藥物]]：[[HMG-CoA_reductase|HMG-CoA reductase]]的競爭性抑制劑，可影響膽固醇合成過程中的速率決定步驟。對HMG-CoA reductase的抑制會使肝臟合成更多LDL受體，使LDL更容易從血液循環內清除。其為降低低密度膽固醇之首選用藥然而需注意其[[肌痛|肌痛]]的不良反應。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=What to Believe and Do About Statin-Associated Adverse Effects|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1001/jama.2016.16557|last=Thompson|first=Paul D.|date=2016-11-15|journal=JAMA|issue=19|doi=10.1001/jama.2016.16557|volume=316|pages=1969|issn=0098-7484}}</ref>

* [[Ezetimibe|Ezetimibe]]：阻斷[[Niemann-Pick_C1-like_1_cholesterol_transfer_protein|Niemann-Pick C1-like 1 cholesterol transfer protein]]，從而抑制腸道和膽道的膽固醇吸收，使肝臟LDL受體表達增加。通常會與他汀類藥物合用<ref>{{Cite web|title=Faculty of 1000 evaluation for Ezetimibe Added to Statin Therapy after Acute Coronary Syndromes.|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.3410/f.725532083.793507596|accessdate=2019-12-31|date=2015-06-21|last=Aronow|first=Wilbert|work=F1000 - Post-publication peer review of the biomedical literature}}</ref>
* [[PCSK9_inhibitor|PCSK9 抑制劑]]：使[[PCSK9_enzyme|PCSK9 enzyme]]失去活性無法分解[[LDL受體|LDL受體]]，從而增加肝細胞上的[[LDL受體|LDL受體]]數量，進而促進血液循環內LDL膽固醇的清除。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mutations in PCSK9 cause autosomal dominant hypercholesterolemia|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/ng1161|last=Abifadel|first=Marianne|last2=Varret|first2=Mathilde|date=2003-05-05|journal=Nature Genetics|issue=2|doi=10.1038/ng1161|volume=34|pages=154–156|issn=1061-4036|last3=Rabès|first3=Jean-Pierre|last4=Allard|first4=Delphine|last5=Ouguerram|first5=Khadija|last6=Devillers|first6=Martine|last7=Cruaud|first7=Corinne|last8=Benjannet|first8=Suzanne|last9=Wickham|first9=Louise}}</ref>
* [[N-3_fatty_acid|N-3 fatty acid]]：可減少肝臟內VLDL的生成並少量增加血液循環內VLDL膽固醇的清除，進而通過這一方式降低血中triglyceride濃度。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Marine n-3 fatty acids and prevention of cardiovascular disease and cancer|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1530/ey.16.12.13|last=JE|first=Manson|last2=NR|first2=Cook|date=2019-09-12|journal=Yearbook of Paediatric Endocrinology|doi=10.1530/ey.16.12.13|issn=1662-4009|last3=IM|first3=Lee|last4=W|first4=Christen|last5=SS|first5=Bassuk|last6=S|first6=Mora|last7=H|first7=Gibson|last8=CM|first8=Albert|last9=D|first9=Gordon}}</ref>

